Class HDBOfficer

Object
User
Applicant
HDBOfficer
public class HDBOfficer extends Applicant
Represents an HDB Officer who is both an applicant and a project handler. Inherits functionality from Applicant and adds features for handling BTO projects, replying to enquiries, booking flats, and generating receipts.
